                        of travel or public exposure.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-serif text-3xl text-gold mb-2">01</p>
                            <p class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-gray-500">Consultation</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
